# This directory contains the ID graph data for Z-ai-graph-viewer consumption.
# See README.md for the API contract and endpoint URLs.
#
# Files in this directory:
# - id-graph.json          : full graph data (committed to repo on every push)
# - id-graph-summary.json  : summary only (for quick dashboards)
# - README.md              : API contract documentation
#
# Visual graphs (SVG/PNG/DOT) are generated to docs/_graph/ instead, since
# they are larger and only needed for static rendering.
